commits.commitMessage:
Implement a set of le_mqttClient APIs

Adds support for the following APIs,

    le_mqttClient_CreateSession()
    le_mqttClient_DeleteSession()
    le_mqttClient_StartSession()
    le_mqttClient_CloseSession()
    le_mqttClient_Publish()
    le_mqttClient_Subscribe()
    le_mqttClient_Unsubscribe()
    le_mqttClient_AddNewMessageHandler()

Resolves: LE-15284
Change-Id: I5b01069cd61ac1aea69cecfe69e6813776550000
